<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="J%20Biomed%20Inform"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Adapting Electronic Health Records-derived Phenotypes to Claims Data: Lessons Learned in Using Limited Clinical Data for Phenotyping</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ostropolets%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Columbia University Medical Center, New York, NY</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Observational Health Data Sciences and Informatics (OHDSI), New York, NY, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ostropolets%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Anna Ostropolets</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>4</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Reich%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Christian Reich</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
